Package: fsort
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-venv, python3-pip, libgl1, libglib2.0-0, ffmpeg
Description: Incremental offline face-based photo and video organizer
 face-sort is a local, offline face organizer with persistent person IDs.
 It only extracts faces from new or modified media, matches them against
 saved person centroids, and clusters remaining unknown faces with DBSCAN.
 .
 This package includes the self-hosted Web UI and systemd services.
